>殺人罪判處皮特絲10年徒刑、棄屍罪為1年半徒刑</span>，合計為11年半，但可獲最多2年的假釋。<br />\n但判決一出，澳洲當地鄉民紛紛挺皮特絲，認為這是一份恐龍判決，網友們紛紛直呼：「皮特絲到底做錯了什麼？對方是性侵犯耶！還威脅要傷害女兒。」許多網友們都希望法官博地斯能「看清楚」，真正犯下大罪的，是性侵犯凱薩，不應對皮特絲下如此重刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181031/640_76fec11be13a2c32785fc5b593952b65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181031%2F640_76fec11be13a2c32785fc5b593952b65.jpg&h=dc348c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181031/1457409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181031%2F1457409&d=QPwT%2ByELcvOQ3V%2B17dE42dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1392653f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181031%2F1457409&h=8714e092\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181031/1457409</a><br />\n<br />\n法官痴線<br />\n<br />\n不過個女應仲正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你又判鳩人殺人罪10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n棄屍年半咋"},{"pid":"9e2770695aa0136913df6de287fb0a681514b5c6","tid":883430,"uid":175108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"942d434b19f4051f380bc42d73af5f1a3e41cf5e","tid":883430,"uid":130901,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"bd81038bc0a435e7de3d4eb1a70bb71c6a678b3b","tid":883430,"uid":142653,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"da447325c62f15e9f347ad777e6841ced56aaa61","tid":883430,"uid":130901,"like":305,"dislike":5,"score":300,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"即時報警唔棄屍其實未必坐監"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T00:34:23.000Z","msg":"答我，如果條女拿住把刀，強姦犯講明只強姦不食害，條女正確做法係咪放低刀比佢姦？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"我記得之前聽過一樣野<br />\n因為要阻止a強姦人而殺左你a<br />\n好似係無罪<br />\n但前提要証明到a真係想強姦人<br />\n而且除左殺佢之外冇其他辦法阻止<br />\n<br />\n但呢